    <https://schema.org/name> "Examen final (temas 1-4)"@es .

# Link Evaluation Trials to System and Guide
<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/evalSystem/GA_08NV_85003112> :hasEvaluationTrial <http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/evalTrial/Control_Temas_1_y_2> ;
